Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:01:01.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,projecting myself a little exaggeratedly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before it all becomes a thing of the past
