Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.95,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.98,0:24:11.71,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
