Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:21.08,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our snooze-time date
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.30,0:24:41.30,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat of your budding warmth troubles me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.06,0:24:52.06,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how I feel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:58.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.95,0:25:04.34,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.37,0:25:10.06,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.09,0:25:15.06,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice)
